Current Objective:

To insert into database and implement delete functionality using checkboxes in frontpage cards
To validate inputs from "add product form" and loop through product types before insertion.

Key Files:

1. index.php - frontpage or product list(Displays data using cards)
2. addproduct.html - to add products to database(uses type switcher to sort product types)
3. Product.php - contains show, insert and delete functions
4. Validator.php - is meant to validate inputs from addproduct form.


